=============================
Standardized test collection
=============================

Here is a collection of standard tests with corresponding 
reference output and necessary input files.


The format for the filenames are

XML FILES (mandatory)
---------------------
(executable).(short test name).xml

REFERENCE FILES (mandatory)
---------------------------
(executable).(short test name).reference.(generating architecture)

INPUT FILES (if necessary)
--------------------------
(executable).(short test name).input




EXAMPLE
-------
test_HMC.my_test.xml
test_HMC.my_test.input
test_HMC.my_test.reference.INTEL
